biography: Dr. Paul Elvers is Head of AI/Data Science at Datadrivers, an IT Consulting Company in Hamburg. He graduated in Systematic Musicology & worked as a Research Fellow at the Max-Planck-Institute for empirical Aesthetics before transitioning into Data Science. He has worked for companies like Tchibo and Smartclip, before joining Datadrivers in 2021.
